channel.title: I need help with Endar v4

[code]Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError: EGUI Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
Can anyone help me with this? I really want to use Endar. :|[br][size=1]Posted on: April 21, 2007, 12:42:05 AM[/size]
[hr]
Fixed the code error. :o
